for _ in range(int(input())):
    (a, b) = map(int, input().split())
    l = 0
    for x in range(a, b + 1):
        c = str(x)
        n = len(c) - 1
        i = 0
        j = 0
        while n >= i:
            if c[i] != c[n]:
                j = 1
                break
            i = i + 1
            n = n - 1
        if j == 0:
            l = l + x
    print(l)

for _ in range(int(input())):
    (l, r) = map(int, input().split(' '))
    ans = 0
    for x in range(l, r + 1):
        x = str(x)
        i = 0
        j = len(x) - 1
        flag = True
        while i <= j:
            if x[i] != x[j]:
                flag = False
                break
            i += 1
            j -= 1
        if flag:
            ans += int(x)
    print(ans)

import sys
for _ in range(int(sys.stdin.readline())):
    (a, b) = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())
    sys.stdout.write(str(sum(filter(lambda x: str(x) == str(x)[::-1], range(a, b + 1)))) + '\n')

t = int(input())
for i in range(t):
    (a, b) = map(int, input().split())
    x = []
    for num in range(a, b + 1):
        digit = str(num)
        digits = digit[::-1]
        if digit == digits:
            z = int(digits)
            x.append(z)
    print(sum(x))
